    <para>
      The filter is derived from the <quote>Cool Metal</quote> script
      (<menuchoice moreinfo="none">
        <guimenu moreinfo="none"><accel>X</accel>tns</guimenu>
        <guisubmenu moreinfo="none"><accel>L</accel>ogo</guisubmenu>
        <guimenuitem moreinfo="none">Cool <accel>M</accel>etal</guimenuitem>
      </menuchoice>
      in the toolbox), which creates a logo from a text as shown above.
    </para>

    

    

    

    
    
